00:50:08,980 --> 00:50:10,640
 neka djeca imaju.

939
00:50:10,640 --> 00:50:11,220
 I onda ono,

940
00:50:11,220 --> 00:50:12,280
 ova koja to imaju,

941
00:50:12,280 --> 00:50:13,480
 brane ovi koji to ne imaju.

942
00:50:13,480 --> 00:50:14,560
 I to je život, ono,

943
00:50:14,560 --> 00:50:14,960
 to je,

944
00:50:14,960 --> 00:50:16,720
 to razvijaš u djeci,

945
00:50:16,720 --> 00:50:18,640
 i naravno da ja nisam za to

946
00:50:18,640 --> 00:50:19,400
 da se djeci vrave,

947
00:50:19,460 --> 00:50:21,360
 da djeca moja tuku drugu djecu u parkiću,

948
00:50:21,360 --> 00:50:22,920
 ali ponekad,

949
00:50:22,920 --> 00:50:23,240
 ovoga,

950
00:50:23,240 --> 00:50:24,360
 ova djeca koja su tako,

951
00:50:24,360 --> 00:50:24,820
 ja kažem,

952
00:50:24,820 --> 00:50:25,180
 ovoga,

953
00:50:25,180 --> 00:50:27,740
 imaju taj dio borilački u sebi,

954
00:50:27,740 --> 00:50:29,300
 onda kažem,

955
00:50:29,300 --> 00:50:29,780
 čuj, ljubi,

956
00:50:29,780 --> 00:50:32,200
 ako vidiš da neko bracu malo tretira,

957
00:50:32,200 --> 00:50:33,740
 dođi pa ga riješi.

958
00:50:33,740 --> 00:50:34,760
 Nema smisla,

959
00:50:34,760 --> 00:50:35,700
 jer danas roditelji isto,

960
00:50:35,700 --> 00:50:36,120
 ovoga,

961
00:50:36,120 --> 00:50:36,880
 piju kavu,

962
00:50:36,880 --> 00:50:38,500
 ući ne gledaju šta im djeca rade u parkiću,

963
00:50:38,500 --> 00:50:40,080
 i onda ja sam više puta intervenirao,

964
00:50:40,080 --> 00:50:40,720
 ono,

965
00:50:40,720 --> 00:50:41,360
 dajte recite,

966
00:50:41,360 --> 00:50:41,720
 dajte,

967
00:50:41,720 --> 00:50:42,500
 pa uduzmite nešto,

968
00:50:42,500 --> 00:50:43,980
 onda se on tebe gledao kao čudaka,

969
00:50:43,980 --> 00:50:49,860
 onda vidiš da stvar mora preći iz tuđe ruke,

970
00:50:49,860 --> 00:50:50,640
 u moju ruku,

971
00:50:50,640 --> 00:50:53,480
 i moja djeca da se brinu u tom dijelu,

972
00:50:53,480 --> 00:50:53,860
 jer gledati,

973
00:50:53,860 --> 00:50:56,140
 ja ne mogu i čokolivu derat se na roditelje,

974
00:50:56,140 --> 00:50:57,800
 ne mogu se derat na drugu djecu,

975
00:50:57,800 --> 00:50:59,300
 to ne znam što nije profesionalno,

976
00:50:59,300 --> 00:51:00,000
 nije normalno,

977
00:51:00,000 --> 00:51:01,080
 tako da,

978
00:51:01,080 --> 00:51:03,220
 podupinem svoju djecu,

979
00:51:03,220 --> 00:51:04,540
 da se obrane,

980
00:51:04,540 --> 00:51:05,500
 i ono što uvrtiću isto,

981
00:51:05,500 --> 00:51:06,400
 tako radimo s djecom,

982
00:51:06,400 --> 00:51:08,460
 da imaju pravo reći stop,

983
00:51:08,460 --> 00:51:11,260
 u tom nekom raspunu svojih ruku,

984
00:51:11,360 --> 00:51:12,760
 i to je ono prva neka reakcija,

985
00:51:12,760 --> 00:51:13,200
 gdje djete,

986
00:51:13,200 --> 00:51:14,260
 to je samo obrana,

987
00:51:14,260 --> 00:51:16,100
 i samo obrana nije napad,

988
00:51:16,100 --> 00:51:17,880
 i braniti svoj osobni prostor nije napad,

989
00:51:17,880 --> 00:51:20,680
 jer vi kasnije u životu se trebate obraniti,

990
00:51:20,680 --> 00:51:22,680
 često ne više fizički,

991
00:51:22,680 --> 00:51:27,100
 ali ako mi od malih nogu ne učemo obraniti sebe i svoj prostor,

992
00:51:27,100 --> 00:51:28,380
 fizički sad trenutno,

993
00:51:28,380 --> 00:51:30,700
 nećemo se ni znati obraniti,

994
00:51:30,700 --> 00:51:33,400
 ni kasnije kad budete ušli u neku vezu s nekim manipulatorom,

995
00:51:33,400 --> 00:51:35,040
 nećete se znati obraniti,

996
00:51:35,040 --> 00:51:36,560
 ako niste to učili obraniti se,

997
00:51:36,560 --> 00:51:38,660
 iako vas nisu roditelje možda u tome,

998
00:51:38,660 --> 00:51:40,640
 kroz neka prijateljstva,

999
00:51:40,640 --> 00:51:42,060
 zašto ta prijateljca je ovakva,

1000
00:51:42,060 --> 00:51:43,340
 zašto ta prijateljca je onakva,

1001
00:51:43,340 --> 00:51:45,520
 zašto se više ne družiš s ovom,

1002
00:51:45,520 --> 00:51:46,240
 zašto ne s onom,

1003
00:51:46,240 --> 00:51:47,720
 ne da vi njima korijete prijateljstvo,

1004
00:51:47,720 --> 00:51:49,760
 nego da vi njima mažda malo otvarate oči,

1005
00:51:49,760 --> 00:51:50,800
 ko je kakav prijatelj,

1006
00:51:50,800 --> 00:51:52,720
 i ko je kako odgojen,

1007
00:51:53,480 --> 00:51:54,960
 ali kažem za sve to treba imati vremena,

1008
00:51:54,960 --> 00:51:56,160
 u kraju krajeva vaše vrijeme,

1009
00:51:56,160 --> 00:51:56,600
