1012
00:52:01,000 --> 00:52:02,620
 pa se bavi terapijom do sada osam,

1013
00:52:02,620 --> 00:52:04,160
 doći kuću u devet,

1014
00:52:04,160 --> 00:52:05,680
 onda gdje je tu moje vrijeme za djecu,

1015
00:52:05,680 --> 00:52:08,360
 gdje je tu mati čuljak muž,

1016
00:52:08,360 --> 00:52:09,820
 i gdje je tu mati čuljak otac.

1017
00:52:09,820 --> 00:52:11,020
 Ok,

1018
00:52:11,020 --> 00:52:14,620
 da se vratim na ono pitanje,

1019
00:52:14,620 --> 00:52:17,060
