1035
00:52:45,040 --> 00:52:46,900
 da bi se to možda trebalo početi naplaćivati,

1036
00:52:46,900 --> 00:52:48,540
 ali ovaj voditelji programa

1037
00:52:48,540 --> 00:52:49,700
 i utemeljati programa,

1038
00:52:49,700 --> 00:52:50,760
