1068
00:53:40,340 --> 00:53:40,700
 a kažem,

1069
00:53:40,700 --> 00:53:41,480
 roditelj s roditeljima

1070
00:53:41,480 --> 00:53:43,120
 to mora ići tako razgovorom,

1071
00:53:43,120 --> 00:53:44,220
 pa sam oni često opiru, da.

1072
00:53:44,220 --> 00:53:47,000
 Da, mislim da je onak nalakše,

1073
00:53:47,000 --> 00:53:48,680
